data.description: Welcome Home to Comfort and Convenience in the Heart of Spring Hill! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a bonus room, nestled in the heart of Spring Hill. This gem offers a host of features that will make every day a joy:  New Sprinkler System: Enjoy lush greenery effortlessly with the convenience of a brand-new sprinkler system, ensuring your garden stays vibrant year-round. Twi 220 Hookups: Whether you have an electric vehicle, a workshop, or other power-hungry needs, this home is ready with two 220 hookups for your convenience. Oversized Corner Lot: Embrace the spaciousness of an oversized corner lot, providing you with ample outdoor space for relaxation, play, or even gardening. Wood Floors in Common Areas: Step into elegance with wood floors gracing the common areas, adding warmth and sophistication to your living space. Spacious Living Room: Gather with family and friends in the generously-sized living room, perfect for creating cherished memories.Spacious Kitchen, Breakfast Nook & Formal Dining Area: Whether it's a quick morning meal or a formal dinner, savor your culinary creations in the charming breakfast nook or the formal dining area.Bonus Room: The extra space is yours to customize--a playroom, home office, or cozy retreat--the possibilities are endless. Pet Washing Tub in Laundry Room: Pamper your furry friends with the convenience of a pet washing tub in the laundry room, making pet care a breeze.Scratch-Resistance Kitchen Appliances: Your kitchen is equipped with modern, scratch-resistant appliances, combining style with durability for easy maintenance. Newer Washer and Dryer: Experience the convenience of a newer washer and dryer, adding efficiency to your laundry routine. Security Cameras/System wired in for convenient transfer. Convenient Location: Situated in the heart of Spring Hill, this home offers easy access to all amenities a buyer could need. From shopping and dining to schools and parks, everything is conveniently within reach. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your home sweet home! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the comfort and convenience that awaits you in Spring Hill.
